    <title>On monomial Golod ideals</title>
    <summary>  We study ideal-theoretic conditions for a monomial ideal to be Golod. For
ideals in a polynomial ring in three variables, our criteria give a complete
characterization. Over such rings, we show that the product of two monomial
ideals is Golod.
</summary>
